Ruza Wenclawska https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruza_Wenclawska 0 Ruza Wenclawska (December 15, 1889 – 1977), also known as Rose Winslow and later as Rose Lyons by marriage, was a Polish-American suffragist, factory inspector and trade union organizer. She also worked as an actress and a poet.
